                            <comment id="12984925" author="wadey" created="Fri, 21 Jan 2011 20:44:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fix JavaScript inheritance.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For Node.js we can use sys.inherits. For browsers, we use Crockford&apos;s inheritance: &lt;a href=&quot;http://javascript.crockford.com/prototypal.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://javascript.crockford.com/prototypal.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
