js fix for IE8 and Firefox 3.6&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12995413" author="wadey" created="Wed, 16 Feb 2011 17:54:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch looks fine to me. I&apos;m curious why this was not working in IE8 or Firefox 3.6 though.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12995477" author="roger.meier" created="Wed, 16 Feb 2011 19:30:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Henrique! Just committed your patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
